career and future.\", \"from\": 977, \"to\": 1060, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a personal choice\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 1001}, {\"ngram\": \"careful consideration\", \"from\": 1014, \"to\": 1035}, {\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1048}, {\"ngram\": \"future\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1059}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's not something I decided on quickly or easily.\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1113, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1081}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I deeply respect Australia and the Aus Cycling Team and it will always be a part of who I am.\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1207, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1131, \"end\": 1140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.5521577484958592, \"rank\": 0.7607833322530514, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 1153, \"end\": 1160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cycling_at_the_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999988567652, \"rank\": 9.778446154227455e-10, \"text\": \"Cycling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cycling_at_the_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cycling_at_the_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a part\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1194}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'As this new chapter in my life begins, I would like to sincerely thank the coaches and support staff who have worked with me over many years in Australia.\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1364, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1354, \"end\": 1363, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.5521577484958592, \"rank\": 0.7607833322530514, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngra