 \"to\": 1499}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I want to say a huge thank you to my teammates for everything we have been through together.\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1631, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my teammates\", \"from\": 1573, \"to\": 1585}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1590, \"to\": 1600}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'You have been there for the highs and the lows, and I am so grateful for all the support, laughter, and hard work we have shared.\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1763, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the highs\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1667}, {\"ngram\": \"the lows\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1680}, {\"ngram\": \"all the support\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1722}, {\"ngram\": \"laughter\", \"from\": 1724, \"to\": 1732}, {\"ngram\": \"hard work\", \"from\": 1738, \"to\": 1747}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'But this decision is about following my passion and pushing myself to new heights.\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1848, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this decision\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1783}, {\"ngram\": \"my passion\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1813}, {\"ngram\": \"new heights\", \"from\": 1836, \"to\": 1847}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'This is not about leaving something behind, but about embracing a new chapter in my journey and chasing a dream, a dream that is to race for the county in which I was born.\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 2023, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1877, \"to\": 1886}, {\"ngram\": \"a new chapter\", \"from\": 1915, \"to\": 1928}, {\"ngram\": \"my journey\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 1942}, {\"ngram\": \"a dream\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 1962}, {\"ngram\": \"a dream\", \"from\": 1964, \"to\": 1971}, {\"ngram\": \"the county\", \"from\": 1992, \"to\": 2002}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I hope you can understand and support me as I continue to give my best in the sport I love.'\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2118, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the